# Testing — engines & deterministic core

- Any package under `packages/domain-*` that implements **deterministic** computation (physiology, bioenergetics, internal load, twin projection) must include **automated tests** (e.g. Vitest) and **golden or fixture inputs** where outputs are numeric or structured.
- Regression tests are required when changing formulas or unit assumptions.
- AI / LLM orchestration layers are not golden-tested for prose; test **contracts**, **tool boundaries**, and **fallback behavior** instead.
